A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Condominiums – Property Insurance Deductibles – Unit Owner Responsibility
3 FOR the purpose of increasing the maximum amount of the council of unit owners’ property
4 insurance deductible for which a unit owner is responsible under certain
5 circumstances; and generally relating to condominium unit owners’ responsibility for
6 the council of unit owners’ insurance deductibles.
